QUARTER_PI - Statische Variable in Klasse pp.util.FloatMath
The value PI/4 as a float. (45 degrees)
quotient(Position, float) - Methode in Schnittstelle pp.util.SegmentLike
Shoots a ray from the specified position in the direction of the specified angle and returns the quotient q such that the intersection point of the ray with the straight line determined by the end points of this segment is at q*from()+(1-q)*to().
quotient1() - Methode in Klasse pp.util.SegmentTest
 
quotient2() - Methode in Klasse pp.util.SegmentTest
 
quotientDist(Position, float) - Methode in Schnittstelle pp.util.SegmentLike
Shoots a ray from the specified position in the direction of the point of this segment with the specified quotient, i.e., the point at q*from()+(1-q)*to(), and returns the distance of the specified position from the intersection point of the ray with the straight line determined by the end points of this segment.
